## Monitoring Infrastructure Setup (15-20 minutes)
**STOP AND WAIT:** Establish monitoring foundation before data collection

### 1. Performance Metrics Framework
**Core Metrics Definition:**
- **System Performance:** Overall system responsiveness and efficiency
- **Workflow Performance:** Individual workflow execution metrics
- **Context Performance:** Context loading, management, and optimization
- **Quality Performance:** Rule effectiveness and user satisfaction
- **Resource Performance:** Token usage, memory, and computational efficiency

**Metrics Hierarchy:**
```
Strategic Metrics (Business Value)
├── Operational Metrics (System Health)
│   ├── Tactical Metrics (Component Performance)
│   │   ├── Execution Metrics (Real-time Performance)
│   │   └── Quality Metrics (Effectiveness Measures)
│   └── Resource Metrics (Efficiency Measures)
└── Predictive Metrics (Future Optimization)
```

### 2. Data Collection Architecture
**Monitoring Data Sources:**
- **Workflow Execution:** Start/end times, success rates, error patterns
- **Context Operations:** Loading times, compression effectiveness, token usage
- **User Interactions:** Response times, error rates, satisfaction scores
- **System Resources:** Memory usage, processing efficiency, storage patterns
- **Quality Metrics:** Rule accuracy, cross-reference validity, update frequency

**Data Collection Points:**
```
performance_monitoring/
├── metrics/                    # Real-time metrics collection
│   ├── system_metrics.json
│   ├── workflow_metrics.json
│   └── context_metrics.json
├── logs/                      # Historical performance logs
│   ├── execution_logs/
│   ├── error_logs/
│   └── optimization_logs/
├── reports/                   # Generated performance reports
│   ├── daily_reports/
│   ├── weekly_reports/
│   └── monthly_reports/
└── alerts/                    # Performance alerts and notifications
    ├── critical_alerts/
    └── optimization_alerts/
```

### 3. Monitoring Integration Points
**System Integration:**
- **Workflow Hooks:** Automatic performance tracking at workflow boundaries
- **Context Managers:** Built-in monitoring for context operations
- **Quality Gates:** Performance validation at quality checkpoints
- **Session Managers:** Session performance tracking and optimization

**Integration Commands:**
- `@performance-start [component]` - Begin performance monitoring for component
- `@performance-checkpoint [label]` - Record performance milestone
- `@performance-report [scope]` - Generate performance report
- `@performance-optimize [target]` - Apply performance optimization

